                <div class="v-app-spec"><span class="v-app-sl">Impedance</span><span class="v-app-sv">&plusmn;8% standard. Tighter tolerance (&plusmn;5%) only on 56&nbsp;GBaud PAM4 transport links.</span></div>
                <div class="v-app-spec"><span class="v-app-sl">Material</span><span class="v-app-sv">Architecture A or full High-Tg FR-4 with selective low-loss on outer pairs for fronthaul/backhaul interfaces.</span></div>
